snippet.title: Diana and Roma celebrate Diana's 8th Birthday Party with Friends!
snippet.description:
Diana is 8 years old! Diana invited all her school friends to celebrate her birthday! It was a super fun day with Friends. Thank you all for your gifts and congratulations!
Thanks for watching!
